/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">順便騎劫下等大家學下英文口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地係咪好憎英文口號? [仲有鳩嗌完香港人加油未?]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1483023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1483023</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:04:13.000Z","msg":"多謝！"},{"pid":"5c87db5c9cb92ee9ae054b8803432025d9ddf8eb","tid":1495353,"uid":80965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:07:32.000Z","msg":"We are Hong Kong!"},{"pid":"3807b787757327de8b63b1b8613452ac825a8b99","tid":1495353,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:07:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a267acb7df8fe4d714a394e8c048ac29d1f0e7cc","tid":1495353,"uid":80965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:08:13.000Z","msg":"They give us corruption!<br />\nWe give them revolution!"},{"pid":"e2d25b0b0f75e9b5b01c2f402c808d8d4bfe521b","tid":1495353,"uid":80965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:09:02.000Z","msg":"最後一句:<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Power to the people!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"07cab7dbad4e2f064eb484ded2a710721b21200a","tid":1495353,"uid":67168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:09:39.000Z","msg":"823"},{"pid":"9951df6227c800804d8cb0a194b6ac16bc5f71a9","tid":1495353,"uid":37234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T05:43:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed6c8eb001efde71228f83ab9f46ceb720f23e1f","tid":1495353,"uid":199438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T06:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373627ae2328d370ae2f7032d2c900e4be8013ea","tid":1495353,"uid":39752,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"784887ec946c218494235d2f46dcb12e8ae86102","tid":1495353,"uid":34676,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:38:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">不要說：文宣組同我煲大佢/ 覺唔覺呢排d文宣少咗好多。 </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">試着說：我地一齊做文宣煲大佢！ </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文宣組係你下屬？？？？？？ <br />\n之前有咁多有心巴打開post講全民文宣，有埋線上網去教大家點做。其實係絕對可以自己做咗先，再掉上個post 到睇下有冇人有建議。而唔係自己講完一大輪，然後結尾講句「文宣組同我煲大佢」就拍下屎忽走左去。<br />\n<br />\n至於有人覺得文宣少咗好多，我諗係因唔係太多人有入到其他文宣公海tg gp，（甚至我仲識人以為所謂既「文宣組」係一個組織嚟，入會要填form）。你自己唔去搵渠道去搵呢d tp，你自己自然就會覺得少。事實係每日文宣都好快手，好多熱心既design系 學生效率極高。喺呢到Shout out 一下文宣組，冇你地呢場運動少一半勝算。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T06:09:50.000Z","msg":"呢個真係必須推<br />\n最撚憎人當文宣老撚奉幫你做嘢"},{"pid":"8f88d752e7271ccc3622fd5a103f7158daeffe5c","tid":1495353,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T06:10:59.000Z","msg":"再推<br />\n<br />\n[突發] 人人都可以做文宣<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1437607\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1437607</a>"},{"pid":"cbb408bbb138ccc36beefb59f7b933e6dce8e32b","tid":1495353,"uid":6003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T06:24:22.000Z","msg":"終於有人詳細講<br />\n其實下下標題黨<br />\n就算你內容寫得幾有point<br />\n都令人無心機睇"},{"pid":"63cce1a172927b5a1841a776d7d5b5eceda7327c","tid":1495353,"uid":6003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T06:30:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"59eeca46b887c25c4b3a400ea474cf0b246d2310","tid":1495353,"uid":309053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T06:39:40.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7997754e1d069846a7629a083642be8bac6f47ea","tid":1495353,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T06:55:37.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但呢刻好難解決<br />\n<br />\n一黎大家好多情緒想發泄，二黎依加大量新post，個標題唔夠搶眼就好快沉<br />\n<br />\n同埋熱門post comment洗得太快，除左頭1版之外其實好難討真係論到，結果大家都係都係正負評-&gt;推post 上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1de1b1f3f8a53e777dbad5794c59829b9936de5","tid":1495353,"uid":50904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T06:58:38.000Z","msg":"互Diu post成日推上熱門我諗係因為真係會留住啲人，不停互相罵黎罵去keep住熱度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46173881f84f1ed2db0a0f4a7851cca9a82529f5","tid":1495353,"uid":84040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T07:04:44.000Z","msg":"不能同意更多<br />\n<br />\n講多一次<br />\n對敵人要不擇手段咁去摧毀佢地<br />\n對同伴要和藹有禮咁去愛護佢地<br />\n<br />\n將所有野負面化唔會對我地有任何好處<br />\n只會不斷打擊我地士氣<br />\n講真，你自己俾人屌就算唔係玻璃心你都唔會好受啦下話<br />\n咁咁樣講野既用意喺邊<br />\n<br />\n連登仔好叻做左好多野<br />\n但有樣野真係要改善<br />\n呢樣野叫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公關</span></strong></span><br />\n好既公關先會得到人支持<br />\n人好多時唔係睇邊個講得岩<br />\n而係睇邊個最得佢歡心"},{"pid":"4d57c5507e766526eb215e35cf8c3aa1be8f0566","tid":1495353,"uid":80965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46173881f84f1ed2db0a0f4a7851cca9a82529f5","tid":1495353,"uid":84040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T07:04:44.000Z","msg":"不能同意更多<br />\n<br />\n講多一次<br />\n對敵人要不擇手段咁去摧毀佢地<br />\n對同伴要和藹有禮咁去愛護佢地<br />\n<br />\n將所有野負面化唔會對我地有任何好處<br />\n只會不斷打擊我地士氣<br />\n講真，你自己俾人屌就算唔係玻璃心你都唔會好受啦下話<br />\n咁咁樣講野既用意喺邊<br />\n<br />\n連登仔好叻做左好多野<br />\n但有樣野真係要改善<br />\n呢樣野叫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公關</span></strong></span><br />\n好既公關先會得到人支持<br />\n人好多時唔係睇邊個講得岩<br />\n而係睇邊個最得佢歡心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T07:20:40.000Z","msg":"做人冇公關食得屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7c3d0db5ed55140ebcfc8853a6592cbf45f3b5","tid":1495353,"uid":84040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu