Time":"2019-08-23T01:16:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1a24ed8588600e3aaa70f09c451d75751444a9a","tid":1495353,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:24:10.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"c8f3a9a3b61df72f0a94cb0b0bf5f83e2c68e970","tid":1495353,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bc90ca1d74c5322ae4c2736a27a0cea233b3aea","tid":1495353,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:19:07.000Z","msg":"老老實實有時上時事台，左一句你地好鬆懈，右一句我地就黎輸，再整多句屌晒你班連登仔<br />\n<br />\n我睇到真係直接閉apps，上黎睇post無啦啦被罵到體無完膚，on99<br />\n<br />\n到時又唔好怪人乜乜物物冇人理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:46:10.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n一上黎就見到個post笑鳩人鏈組會唔成<br />\n心情即刻一沉，放棄繼續睇post<br />\n<br />\n可能我心靈脆弱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc064eba24b109bcebf66a2501a83b4eaffd1259","tid":1495353,"uid":26138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:56:07.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"adf2eadcbb501a0acfe12dab1b84655ccdfe1188","tid":1495353,"uid":306548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:58:37.000Z","msg":"Agger <br />\n果種寫法同中共中意將啲嘢掉轉黎講有咩分別<br />\n依家咁多市民都會上連登 我老母(黃絲反共)系其中一個<br />\n會比呢啲標題黨搞到一頭霧水<br />\n同埋有啲內容極負面純粹宣涉情緒咁<br />\n我地應該要比人睇到香港人唔止高IQ<br />\n仲要高EQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bfa0955598523e8f059e86b2cde124c54eac2a1","tid":1495353,"uid":6308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:09:43.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"249fe0b278da39041406523568cacaf416581152","tid":1495353,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:31:39.000Z","msg":"唉屌，結果又犯賤上黎<br />\n<br />\n一黎見到個post類似「我係義士都對你地心淡」<br />\n又冇啦啦被人屌，真係戒上連登算，影響晒心情<br />\n<br />\n我肯定外人肯定會頂唔順，每日屌屌屌，屌政府唔緊要，屌上黎睇post既手足係做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175e8a446d8554546ad9cf35ff2d99baea32808f","tid":1495353,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"261216b449276235542faff69ad4ce8805172e1a","tid":1495353,"uid":34676,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:42:05.000Z","msg":"如果係平時對住圍內人既話，我絕對唔介意呢d高登風格。<br />\n但由6月開始，已經愈嚟愈多人上連登，我仲主動叫我親戚上嚟了解，我淺黃老豆都有上，佢同我講每日都輸輸輸睇到唔想上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:39:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ZudLX07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZudLX07.jpg&h=5fb14145&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港電影欠香港人一場革命<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497679\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497679</a>"},{"pid":"f42584244d6d5ef062edc7508bf664428b62fb7a","tid":1495353,"uid":26138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:30:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"716ea1e3d8e159bd4229bdde30af4bbb4b5114b6","tid":1495353,"uid":245523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:34:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1a4e36cef593ea98f76dee39a03b51146e2ee8a5","tid":1495353,"uid":101378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:47:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b65bbf7494b771fcdfb036d83bf6eba7d9735b1b","tid":1495353,"uid":73619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:02:16.000Z","msg":"請每日重post, 長期置頂"},{"pid":"1a5447d55e5e9dd8aa06305d25171926a0bbb3ca","tid":1495353,"uid":39470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:23:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39ea655134c4913948eb12ed0537a944eaa59568","tid":1495353,"uid":3947